Module Rendering

Module Summary
Rendering Given a scene constructed by the animation module, the rendering module will convert it into an attractive, high-quality video. This will involve code to handle texturing and lighting. The rendering module will also specify the settings for the rendering process and automate the generation of the output file..
 

Procedure Summary
void sceneRenderer()
render a scene. Please be patient. It may take a while.
